<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>OCEL</title>
     {% block stylesheets %}
            {{ encore_entry_link_tags('app') }}
        {% endblock %}

        {% block javascripts %}
            {{ encore_entry_script_tags('app') }}
           
        {% endblock %}
</head>
<body>
    <header class="d-flex justify-content-center bg-white" >
        <img src="{{asset("/images/logo.png")}}" alt="logo" class="img-fluid" style="width:800px;height:150px">
    </header>
    <div class="container-fluid bg-secondary py-2">
        <ul class="nav flex-column flex-sm-row justify-content-center" >
            <li class="nav-item">
                <a class="nav-link text-white btn btn-secondary" href="{{path("app_apropos")}}">A propos</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
                <a class="nav-link text-white btn btn-secondary" href="{{path("app_contact")}}">Nous contacter</a>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="row mt-3">
        <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-8 col-12">
            <img src="{{asset("/images/logo.png")}}" alt="logo" class="img-fluid h-50 w-100">
            <p class="mt-3 px-3">
                Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Ex sit vero eos, asperiores quibusdam earum dignissimos modi, quisquam, iste quos pariatur sed similique iure dolorem alias quo? Dolores, nobis reiciendis.
                Numquam ratione quisquam sed sint recusandae quibusdam expedita ipsam iste, cum reiciendis explicabo culpa alias maxime laboriosam ea quas odit quo voluptates neque? At sint nobis consectetur eligendi labore sit?
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-4 col-12 px-5">
            <div class="px-5 mx-5 mt-5 border rounded rounded-3 shadow-lg py-3 ">
                <form method="post">
                    {% if error %}
                        <div class="alert alert-danger">{{ error.messageKey|trans(error.messageData, 'security') }}</div>
                    {% endif %}
                    {% if app.user %}
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            Connecter en tant que {{ app.user.userIdentifier }}, <a href="{{ path('app_logout') }}">Logout</a>
                        </div>
                    {% endif %}

                    <p class="h3 mb-3 font-weight-normal text-center">Connexion</p>
                    <input type="text" value="{{ last_username }}" name="username" id="inputUsername" placeholder="nom d'utilisateur" class="form-control my-3" autocomplete="username" required autofocus>
                
                    <input type="password" name="password" id="inputPassword" placeholder="mot de passe" class="form-control my-3" autocomplete="current-password" required>

                    <input type="hidden" name="_csrf_token"
                        value="{{ csrf_token('authenticate') }}"
                    >
                    <hr>
                    <button class="btn btn-lg text-white" style="background-color : #0F3170" type="submit">
                        Connexion
                    </button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
